properties.description: We are part of the international 'Men's Shed' movement and meet twice a week to enjoy practical making and mending activities - usually items for community benefit. We have large and well-equipped workshop spaces and a warm social space for relaxing, games, and putting the world to rights over a cuppa and a biscuit. We welcome anyone to call in for a warm-up, a chat and a hot drink on us during these chilly months.

It’s a place where you can come in from the cold and enjoy a hot drink, some soup, and play some board games – and the best part is – It’s completely free!
